These are Puzzles for 4x6 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: sunflower, bellflower, poppy, lily, balloon-flower, begonia
There are 6 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ivory, yellow, lavender, azure, white
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, zombie, drama, sports, spy, crime
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, ship, skateboard, trike, van
 1. the person who likes ivory is the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
 3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 5. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 7. the person who growslily is the person driving the ship##1
 8. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 9. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
10. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
11. the person who growspoppy is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
13. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the ship##2
14. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
15. the person watching sports movies is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who growsbegonia is the person watching spy movies##1
17. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
18. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
19. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
20. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
21. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |         3          |      4       |     5     |     6     |
| Flower        | lily | balloon-flower     | begonia          | sunflower    | bellflower   | poppy    |
| Color         | ivory     | yellow | white | lavender | azure | fuchsia |
| Movie-Genre         | sports        | zombie       | spy              | crime       | drama    | comedy      |
| Transport   | ship        | jet-ski   | skateboard         | van          | trike     | boat      |

