.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-3-13::.
There 6 different types of food: orange, peach, strawberry, pumpkin, asparagus, lettuce
6 different games are played: billiard, go, backgammon, whist, canasta, poker
There are 6 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, sprite, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, bike, quad-bike, scooter, taxi, train
 1. the person driving the airplane is the person playing billiard##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the bike is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 7. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
11. the person eating asparagus is the person playing go##1
12. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
13. the person driving the bike is the person playing canasta##1
14. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
15. the person playing whist is the person driving the train##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
17. the person playing whist is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
18. the person drinking tea is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2       |     3      |       4       |     5      |         6          |
| Food           | asparagus | pumpkin    | strawberry | peach  | orange      | lettuce |
| Game   | go     | canasta       | whist   | backgammon      | poker    | billiard         |
| Beverage         | fanta      | hot-chocolate | coffee     | almond-milk | tea | sprite           |
| Transport     | scooter       | bike         | train      | quad-bike     | taxi       | airplane           |

