The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, family, satire, superhero, thriller, time-travel
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: orchid, azalea, poppy, marigold, iris, zinnia
 1. the person who growsiris is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 4. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the russian##3
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the british##1
 6. the person driving the van is on the right of the british##1
 7. the british is the person who growsiris##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is the person watching superhero movies##1
10. the person who growspoppy is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
12. the russian is on the left or right of the british##3
13. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the indian##3
14. the french is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
15. the australian is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
16. the person who growsorchid is the person watching satire movies##1
17. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
18. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
