6 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, mouse, chinchilla, horse, hamster
The people use 6 different means of transport: bus, car, roller, scooter, skateboard, taxi
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person traveling to boston and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the rabbit##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person driving the roller##2
 9. the person traveling to hannover is the person driving the roller##1
10. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
11. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
12. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
13. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
14. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's sport is basketball and the owner of the horse##2
15. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
16. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
17. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
