 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 8. the person eating pineapple is the owner of the lizard##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
10. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
11. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
12. the person eating lime is the person playing poker##1
