 8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the fan of techno##1
 9. the videographer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
10. the doctor is the person who's sport is baseball##1
11. the police-officer is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
12. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
13. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is doctoring##1
14. the fan of reggae is on the left of the electrician##1
15. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who's sport is golf##1
16. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
17. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the dressmaker##1
